Title:
KFC has a new competitor in India .  
                    WOW chicken !!!
sport_event: ['Six Nations', 'Winter Paralympics', 'ODI World Cup for women']
Festivals: ['Glasgow International Film Festival 2022', 'Santa Barbara International Film Festival 2022']
Narrative:
Kolkata boy Sagar Daryani , who made his entreprenuial debut with the launch of QSR ( quick service restaurant) brand WOW ! momo at the age of 21 has devised a strategy to make American player KFC ; his answer : WOW chicken outlets across cities in the next couple of years. 
At a tome when a spate of local new age companies are banking relatively affordable D2C model _ thanks to the online boom, to compete with established Indian and global brands and widen the localized choice for consumers , the reasoning behind Daryani's move to pit his brand against KFC is very hard to surmise.
